name: Dark Hummingbird
description: A dark hummingbird theme, I started off with Gray Hummingbird and merged a few bits of Hummingbird Fixes into it. I've since added in a bit of my own style into it. everything should be at least readable, I still need to tweak bits of contrast in areas.
